[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 2.219,
    "text": "Our next guest may have perfect attendance."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.22,
    "endTime": 5.52,
    "text": "But one thing she does not have is a perfect attendance pencil."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.52,
    "endTime": 6.63,
    "text": "Take a look."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.63,
    "endTime": 9.49,
    "text": "Yesterday, I put my pencil--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.49,
    "endTime": 13.02,
    "text": "my pink, perfect attendance pencil-- in the sharpen box."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.02,
    "endTime": 15.959,
    "text": "But when I unpacked, I went to go get my pencil."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.96,
    "endTime": 18.206,
    "text": "And guess what I saw?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.206,
    "endTime": 21.7,
    "text": "Nothing but yellow, plain old pencils."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.7,
    "endTime": 23.43,
    "text": "Somebody-- and I know who--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.43,
    "endTime": 26.009,
    "text": "stole my perfect attendance pencil,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.01,
    "endTime": 30.090000000000003,
    "text": "who didn't even earn one, because they were in Canada!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.09,
    "endTime": 32.84,
    "text": "And then Reese jumped in and said, yeah, she earned it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.84,
    "endTime": 33.870000000000005,
    "text": "You didn't earn it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.87,
    "endTime": 36.72,
    "text": "You were in Canada!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.72,
    "endTime": 39.18,
    "text": "And then-- well, she didn't say it like that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.18,
    "endTime": 41.88,
    "text": "She was like, you were in Canada."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.88,
    "endTime": 44.473,
    "text": "Your cute little outfit, and your cute little bows"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.473,
    "endTime": 46.14,
    "text": "in your hair, and your cute little hair,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.14,
    "endTime": 47.28,
    "text": "and your cute little self."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.28,
    "endTime": 48.54,
    "text": "Thank you, Ellen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.54,
    "endTime": 49.26,
    "text": "Hi."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.26,
    "endTime": 50.489,
    "text": "So OK, tell me about this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.49,
    "endTime": 52.050000000000004,
    "text": "This seems very upsetting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.05,
    "endTime": 56.068999999999996,
    "text": "So you had the perfect attendance pencil."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.07,
    "endTime": 57.15,
    "text": "And then it was gone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.15,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "And on a scale of 1 to 10, how mad were you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.0,
    "endTime": 64.33,
    "text": "I would say 10, because I earned the pencil,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.33,
    "endTime": 67.39,
    "text": "and I really liked that pencil."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.39,
    "endTime": 71.31,
    "text": "I was pink, and then it had a pink eraser."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.31,
    "endTime": 75.85000000000001,
    "text": "It was real big, because I never used the eraser."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.85,
    "endTime": 79.72,
    "text": "And it had rainbows, and it said \"Attendance Award.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.72,
    "endTime": 80.76,
    "text": "Oh, wait."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.76,
    "endTime": 82.72,
    "text": "You had never used the eraser?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.72,
    "endTime": 83.46,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.46,
    "endTime": 83.97,
    "text": "Wow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.97,
    "endTime": 85.74,
    "text": "So you never made a mistake?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.74,
    "endTime": 88.33,
    "text": "That's amazing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.33,
    "endTime": 89.164,
    "text": "Anyway."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.164,
    "endTime": 91.915,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.915,
    "endTime": 94.29,
    "text": "So is this the first time you've had a perfect attendance"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.29,
    "endTime": 95.22000000000001,
    "text": "pencil?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.22,
    "endTime": 97.5,
    "text": "No, I get one every year."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.5,
    "endTime": 99.094,
    "text": "Oh, you do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.094,
    "endTime": 101.082,
    "text": "Wow, that's amazing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.082,
    "endTime": 104.56099999999999,
    "text": "[CHEERING]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172800.0,
    "endTime": 0.0,
    "text": "00:01:45,070 --> 00:01:45,990 That's amazing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.99,
    "endTime": 109.149,
    "text": "OK, and so talk me through this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.15,
    "endTime": 112.09,
    "text": "When did you realize it was missing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.09,
    "endTime": 116.8,
    "text": "So we sat in the cafeteria, and then we went to the class."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.8,
    "endTime": 119.509,
    "text": "And I unpacked, got my morning workout,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.51,
    "endTime": 122.35000000000001,
    "text": "and then I went to look in the--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.35,
    "endTime": 123.309,
    "text": "You got what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.31,
    "endTime": 125.23,
    "text": "My morning workout."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.23,
    "endTime": 126.43,
    "text": "Oh, I thought you were--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.43,
    "endTime": 127.33000000000001,
    "text": "your morning workout."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.33,
    "endTime": 128.663,
    "text": "Like, you did sit-ups and stuff."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.663,
    "endTime": 130.94,
    "text": "OK, you got your morning workout."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.94,
    "endTime": 132.06,
    "text": "OK, go ahead."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.06,
    "endTime": 135.38,
    "text": "And then I looked in the sharpen bin,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.38,
    "endTime": 139.26,
    "text": "where my pencil usually is, and it was gone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.26,
    "endTime": 143.679,
    "text": "And then I went to my desk just to use the plain pencil."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.68,
    "endTime": 145.79000000000002,
    "text": "I looked behind me, and I saw Lizzie had"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.79,
    "endTime": 148.12,
    "text": "my perfect attendance pencil."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.12,
    "endTime": 148.93,
    "text": "OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.93,
    "endTime": 152.29000000000002,
    "text": "And then did you say, Lizzie, can I have my pencil back?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.29,
    "endTime": 156.64,
    "text": "Yes, I did, but she said, just go get a regular pencil."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.64,
    "endTime": 158.23,
    "text": "It's just a pencil."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.23,
    "endTime": 159.73,
    "text": "I found it in the pencil bin."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.73,
    "endTime": 161.04899999999998,
    "text": "Right, yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 161.05,
    "endTime": 162.97,
    "text": "But it wasn't just a regular pencil to you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.97,
    "endTime": 164.17,
    "text": "It was a special pencil."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.17,
    "endTime": 164.67,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.67,
    "endTime": 166.48,
    "text": "So how did you finally get the pencil back?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.48,
    "endTime": 167.709,
    "text": "What happened?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.71,
    "endTime": 171.73000000000002,
    "text": "Well, I asked for it back right before lunch."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.73,
    "endTime": 173.32,
    "text": "She said, sure."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.32,
    "endTime": 178.09,
    "text": "But she lost the pencil somewhere."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.09,
    "endTime": 180.0,
    "text": "And then she said after recess, but I never"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.0,
    "endTime": 181.91,
    "text": "got it back after recess."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.91,
    "endTime": 182.57,
    "text": "OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.57,
    "endTime": 184.85,
    "text": "Autumn found it the next day, and then I"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.85,
    "endTime": 185.75,
    "text": "told her it was mine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.75,
    "endTime": 187.55,
    "text": "She gave it straight to me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.55,
    "endTime": 189.14000000000001,
    "text": "Oh, Ana gave it straight to you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.14,
    "endTime": 190.22199999999998,
    "text": "That's really nice of Ana."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.223,
    "endTime": 191.06,
    "text": "Autumn."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.06,
    "endTime": 191.938,
    "text": "I'm sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.938,
    "endTime": 195.35,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 331200.0,
    "endTime": 0.0,
    "text": "00:03:15,850 --> 00:03:17,560 I was thinking of Ana, who--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.56,
    "endTime": 199.052,
    "text": "she's no longer there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.052,
    "endTime": 200.29,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.29,
    "endTime": 200.959,
    "text": "Autumn."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.96,
    "endTime": 201.46,
    "text": "Autumn."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.46,
    "endTime": 203.05,
    "text": "Yeah, that was very sweet of her, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.05,
    "endTime": 203.55,
    "text": "Mm-hmm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.55,
    "endTime": 204.47,
    "text": "Yeah, good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.47,
    "endTime": 207.227,
    "text": "OK, and so you're not there today."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.227,
    "endTime": 209.56,
    "text": "Today is Wednesday, and you're supposed to be at school."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.56,
    "endTime": 212.08,
    "text": "So I got you a letter that you can bring back, because you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.08,
    "endTime": 213.08,
    "text": "want perfect attendance."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.08,
    "endTime": 215.02700000000002,
    "text": "So I just signed a letter that tells them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.027,
    "endTime": 216.10899999999998,
    "text": "why you weren't there, OK?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.11,
    "endTime": 216.818,
    "text": "Thank you, Ellen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.818,
    "endTime": 218.90200000000002,
    "text": "OK, because I want you to have perfect attendance."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.902,
    "endTime": 219.45899999999997,
    "text": "OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.46,
    "endTime": 221.20700000000002,
    "text": "I got something for your entire class,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.207,
    "endTime": 223.54,
    "text": "because they're going to be so jealous that you're here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.54,
    "endTime": 226.57,
    "text": "Because everybody is going to be like, oh, Taylor's on Ellen,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.57,
    "endTime": 227.57,
    "text": "and we didn't get to go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.57,
    "endTime": 229.305,
    "text": "So I wanted to give them something."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.305,
    "endTime": 230.68,
    "text": "So let me show you what I'm going"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.68,
    "endTime": 234.1,
    "text": "to get for the whole class--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 234.1,
    "endTime": 237.67,
    "text": "all kinds of supplies, and pencils, and different things"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.67,
    "endTime": 238.29899999999998,
    "text": "for everybody."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.3,
    "endTime": 240.0,
    "text": "They're going to thank you so much for that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.0,
    "endTime": 240.0,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.0,
    "endTime": 244.29,
    "text": "Lizzie and Autumn are going to be like, right on, girl."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244.29,
    "endTime": 247.005,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 247.005,
    "endTime": 248.38,
    "text": "And then I got something for you,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.38,
    "endTime": 250.03,
    "text": "too-- something really special that I"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.03,
    "endTime": 251.204,
    "text": "think you're going to like."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.204,
    "endTime": 253.14000000000001,
    "text": "You're not going to lose this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 253.14,
    "endTime": 256.527,
    "text": "[CHEERING]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 460800.0,
    "endTime": 0.0,
    "text": "00:04:20,884 --> 00:04:21,836 Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.836,
    "endTime": 262.336,
    "text": "Look."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 471600.0,
    "endTime": 0.0,
    "text": "00:04:25,260 --> 00:04:27,110 You're not going to lose that one, are you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.11,
    "endTime": 267.61,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.61,
    "endTime": 269.25,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.25,
    "endTime": 271.74,
    "text": "We're going to have to get you a big backpack, though."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.74,
    "endTime": 272.58,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.58,
    "endTime": 273.3,
    "text": "All right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.3,
    "endTime": 274.8,
    "text": "All right, we'll be right back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.8,
    "endTime": 277.5,
    "text": "Before we go, I want to talk to Taylor about one more thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.5,
    "endTime": 279.86,
    "text": "Taylor, will you come back down here?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.86,
    "endTime": 283.29,
    "text": "[CHEERING]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.29,
    "endTime": 286.72,
    "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 514800.0,
    "endTime": 0.0,
    "text": "00:04:49,952 --> 00:04:51,660 I forgot, I was going to ask you what you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 291.66,
    "endTime": 292.91,
    "text": "want to do when you get older."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 292.91,
    "endTime": 294.952,
    "text": "Do you know what you want to be when you grow up?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 294.952,
    "endTime": 295.53,
    "text": "Yes, I do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 295.53,
    "endTime": 296.488,
    "text": "What do you want to do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.488,
    "endTime": 298.176,
    "text": "I want to be a science teacher."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 298.176,
    "endTime": 299.01,
    "text": "A s--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 299.01,
    "endTime": 300.0,
    "text": "I like science."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 300.0,
    "endTime": 301.212,
    "text": "Yeah?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301.212,
    "endTime": 302.14,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 302.14,
    "endTime": 303.5,
    "text": "What do you like about science?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 303.5,
    "endTime": 305.95,
    "text": "You get to do all these cool experiments."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 305.95,
    "endTime": 306.45,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306.45,
    "endTime": 308.69,
    "text": "And you never know what's going to happen,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308.69,
    "endTime": 311.0,
    "text": "but something cool always happens."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 311.0,
    "endTime": 312.38,
    "text": "Yeah, science is very cool."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 312.38,
    "endTime": 313.159,
    "text": "That's great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 313.16,
    "endTime": 314.93,
    "text": "Well, here's what I want to do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 314.93,
    "endTime": 317.3,
    "text": "I love that you care about school so much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 317.3,
    "endTime": 320.24,
    "text": "And Shutterfly loves that you have perfect attendance,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 320.24,
    "endTime": 322.76,
    "text": "so they're going to give you a $10,000 scholarship"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 322.76,
    "endTime": 323.39,
    "text": "to make sure--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 323.39,
    "endTime": 324.602,
    "text": "[CHEERING]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 324.602,
    "endTime": 328.592,
    "text": "--you go to college."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.592,
    "endTime": 330.8,
    "text": "I want to thank, Charles Barkley, the Jonas Brothers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 330.8,
    "endTime": 331.385,
    "text": "I'll see you tomorrow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 331.385,
    "endTime": 332.603,
    "text": "Be kind to one another."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 332.603,
    "endTime": 333.53000000000003,
    "text": "Bye."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 333.53,
    "endTime": 334.267,
    "text": "Hi, I'm Andy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 334.267,
    "endTime": 336.6,
    "text": "Ellen asked me to remind you to subscribe to her channel"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336.6,
    "endTime": 338.47,
    "text": "so you can see more awesome videos,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 338.47,
    "endTime": 341.68,
    "text": "like videos of me getting scared or saying embarrassing things,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 341.68,
    "endTime": 344.43,
    "text": "like ball peen hammer, and also some videos of Ellen"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 344.43,
    "endTime": 347.23,
    "text": "and other celebrities, if you're into that sort of thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 347.23,
    "endTime": 347.73,
    "text": "[SHOUTS]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 347.73,
    "endTime": 349.83000000000004,
    "text": "[SCREAMS] [BLEEP] God!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 349.83,
    "endTime": 351.38,
    "text": "[BLEEP]"
  }
]